name: Snow Creek (West Fork)
description:
Introduction

NOTE: I have found there is another Snow Creek in Northern California also posted on this site. This one is located in the San Jacinto Mountains near Palm Springs.

A legal route to a canyon on the North Side of Mt San Jacinto by using the PCT for ingress & egress.

Snow Creek is gauged, so the Waterflow Analysis will tell you EXACTLY how much water you will find.
